Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: input-from-web
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.12),
         python3-flask,
         python3-qrcode,
         ydotool,
         wl-clipboard
Description: Phone voice dictation to Linux desktop input
 Use your phone's voice-to-text to type into any focused app on your
 Linux desktop. Runs a small web server, generates a QR code with a
 secure URL, and injects received text via ydotool or wl-clipboard.
